{
  "chapter": 38,
  "chapter_summary": "本章围绕绝情谷、断肠崖与十六年之约展开。郭襄随众追寻神雕侠踪迹，逐渐触及杨过和小龙女生死离合的旧事；黄蓉当年以南海神尼之说留下希望，使杨过苦守十六年。众人重入绝情谷，昔日情花毒、公孙氏恩怨、慈恩与瑛姑旧仇皆被重新牵起。杨过在断肠崖前由希望转入绝望，又因小龙女留下的线索和众人的劝阻，在生死边缘徘徊。全章以旧怨消解、深情未断和重逢悬念为核心，为后续杨龙相会及群雄重聚铺垫。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要拦阻，好好拦阻便了，如何这般不三不四，戏耍姑娘？\n\n",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小心了！\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊哟！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "白母",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "绿母",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老和尚的本领当真不小，就可惜不做好事。\n\n",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既羡慕我的本领，只须拜我为师，我便将这一身功夫，尽数传你。\n\n",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭襄心想这些功夫当真好玩，但这老和尚是恶人，怎能拜他为师，再者自己急于要找杨过，摇头说道：",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n国师道：",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guo",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭襄道：",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "国师笑道：",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "国师道：",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n国师摇头道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭襄恼道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "国师说道：",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "国师冲口而出：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guo",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭襄道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n她这番话其实乃随口编造，只不过意欲气气国师，别说英雄大宴中商议的是如何守襄阳、抗蒙古，就真有人论到国师和杨过武功优劣，郭襄未曾与会，也不会听到。\n\n岂知这话正好刺中了国师的痛处。他十余年前果曾数度败在杨过手下，只道天下英雄确是以此作为话柄，熬不住满腔怒火如焚，喝道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guo",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n郭襄心念一动，道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "国师抢着道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guo",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n国师岂不知郭襄在使激将之计，但他一生自视极高，偏生确曾败于杨过手下，此番将",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guo",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "练到了第十层，原是要找杨过一报昔年大败之辱，大声道：",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guo",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭襄哈哈大笑，拍手唱道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我虽不知杨过此时身在何方，但再过二个多月，他定要到一个处所，我却知道。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到什么地方？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "跟你说了有什么用？\n\n你又不敢去见他，徒然吓得你魂不附体。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说，你说！\n\n",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他要到绝情谷去，要在断肠崖前和他妻子小龙女相会。\n\n一个杨过已叫你心惊肉跳，再加上一个小龙女，嘿嘿，老和尚啊，你又何苦到断肠崖去送死？\n\n就算他们夫妻重会，心中欢喜，不想杀人，你大败亏输之后，也难免伤心断肠了。\n\n",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guo",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "龙象般若功",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guo",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "玉女素心剑法",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guo",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭襄道：",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "国师笑道：",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guo",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "玉女素心剑法",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你师父自有对付他们的法子。\n\n不过杨过既是你大哥哥，你师父跟他化敌为友，再见到时大家做好朋友便了。\n\n",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那很好，师父，你打不过我大哥哥，还是跟他做好朋友比较聪明。\n\n",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怎么会打他不过？只不过我已练成了第十层的龙象般若功，一出手就把你大哥哥打死了，你一定要大哭大叫，我不舍得你悲伤，因此不打死他。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你倒好心肠，我多谢你了！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "国师道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n打开帐篷角里一个大红羊毛毡的包袱，取出一个卷轴，展了开来，帛上用细丝线绣着一位站在云雾中的神仙般人物，头戴红色法冠，左手持一朵粉红色莲花，右手持剑，斩向一团乱丝。\n\n国师道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我从今天起，教你修报身佛金刚萨埵所说的瑜伽密乘，修成之后，再修法身佛普贤菩萨所说的大瑜伽密乘、无比瑜伽密乘，一直到最后的无上瑜伽密乘。\n\n",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师父，要修成无上瑜伽密乘，那得多少时候啊？\n\n",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无上瑜伽密乘无穷无尽，永远说不上修成，也说不上要多少时候。\n\n",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那你也没修成了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是啊，倘若我修得稍有成就，怎么还会去苦练那龙象般若功？\n\n还会起心来和杨过、小龙女决一胜败？真是蠢才！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁说你蠢了？\n\n不决一胜败，又怎知谁蠢谁聪明？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我先教你六字大明咒：唵、嘛、呢、叭、咪、吽，你诚心诚意跟我念一遍。\n\n",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "国师问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "心道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n国师口念密宗真言，盼求上师慈悲加持，感化郭襄发心去修学瑜伽密乘。\n\n他这一派的教法，讲究缘法以及修习者的诚意发愿，外人不得勉强，他那知郭襄这时心中想的却是：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_ying",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉叹了一口气，并不言语。三人离了渡口，再往郊外闲走。\n\n这一日艳阳和暖，南风薰人，虽在北国，也有些十月小阳春之意。\n\n晋南一带，一到冬天便无甚花卉，这日到了山阳，高山挡住了北风，气候温暖，黄蓉忽见一堵断垣下开着一丛花，颜色娇艳，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_ying",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "陆无双道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_wu_shuang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因程英叫黄蓉",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_ying",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "，陆无双硬要高郭芙一辈，便跟着也叫",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么叫'断肠花'？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "从前有个姑娘，想着她的情郎，那情郎不来，这姑娘常常泪洒墙下。\n\n后来墙下开了一丛花，叶子绿，背面红，很是美丽，他们说，只在背后才红，无情得很，因此叫它'断肠花'。\n\n",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_wu_shuang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这似乎是小龙女所养的玉蜂，怎地在此出现？\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_wu_shuang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，咱们便跟着这蜜蜂，瞧它飞向何处？\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老顽童，你瞧是谁来啦！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老顽童，老顽童，怎地见了远客，反躲将起来？\n\n",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不开，不开！\n\n死也不开！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不开门，我一把火将你的狗窝烧成了灰。\n\n",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "荒山光降贵客，老和尚恭迎。\n\n",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来大师和老顽童作了邻居，真想不到。\n\n老顽童不知何故，突然拒客，闭门不纳？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "且莫理他！\n\n三位请进，待老僧奉茶。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭夫人，你猜上一猜，那右首茅屋中住的是谁？\n\n",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n当晚黄蓉等三人都在锳姑的茅屋歇宿。翌晨黄蓉起身，走出屋外，见周伯通手掌中托着一只玉蜂，手舞足蹈，得意非凡。\n\n黄蓉笑道：",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 415,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n周伯通笑道：",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 415,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n黄蓉素知他生平但有两好，一是玩闹，一是武学，这十余年来隐居荒谷，潜心练武，想来又有什么",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 415,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "之类古怪高明的武功创了出来，倒也颇想见识见识，说道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 415,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n黄蓉心中暗暗称奇：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 415,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n周伯通手掌高举，托着那只玉蜂，洋洋自得，说道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉撇嘴道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n黄蓉哈哈大笑，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通也不生气，笑嘻嘻的道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说着将左掌伸到黄蓉眼前。\n\n只见他掌心中托着那只巨蜂的双翅之上果然刺得有字，黄蓉凝目望去，见玉蜂右翅上有",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三字，左翅上有",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三字，每个字细如米粒，但笔划清楚，显是用极细的针刺成。\n\n黄蓉大奇，口中喃喃念道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "心想：",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一转念间，笑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n周伯通一听，登时胀红了脸，说道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉笑道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拉着她走到山坡边一个蜂巢旁边。这蜂巢孤另另的竖在一旁，与其余的蜂巢不在一起。\n\n周伯通手一扬，捉了两只玉蜂，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 473,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉凝目看去，见一只玉蜂翅上无字，另一只双翅上有字，那六个字也一模一样，右翅是",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 473,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "，左翅是",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 473,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "。\n\n黄蓉大奇，暗想：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 473,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通又捉了四只，其中两只翅上无字，另外两只双翅都刺着这六个字。\n\n他见黄蓉低头沉吟，显已服输，不敢再说是锳姑所为，笑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 473,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "心中怦怦乱跳，侧头向周伯通道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 495,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n周伯通脸上一红，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 495,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 495,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 495,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉沉吟道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 495,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n黄蓉沉吟半晌，回到茅屋，和一灯大师、程英、陆无双等商议，都觉绝情谷底必有跷蹊。\n\n黄蓉挂念女儿，当下便要和程陆姊妹同去一探。一灯大师道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 495,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_da_shi",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉当即拜谢，心中却平添一层隐忧：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 495,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_ying",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "龙女花",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "line_start": 533,
      "line_end": 545
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_long_nv",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大智岛南海神尼",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 533,
      "line_end": 545
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_long_nv",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他一啸之威，震狮倒虎，这几句话发自肺腑，只震得山谷皆鸣，但听得群山响应，东南西北，四周山峰都传来：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 585,
      "line_end": 605
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不守信约，你不守信约！\n\n",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "line_start": 621,
      "line_end": 635
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥哥，我来啦！\n\n",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "line_start": 637,
      "line_end": 649
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这里还有你的一枚金针，须听我话，千万不可自尽⋯⋯",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "line_start": 637,
      "line_end": 649
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "倒挂金钩",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 637,
      "line_end": 649
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "国师道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 667,
      "line_end": 683
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说着将郭襄的半幅衣袖一扬。\n\n黄蓉瞧那衣袖，果真是从女儿的衣上撕下，这一来犹如身入冰窟，全身发颤，说不出话来。\n\n周伯通怒道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 667,
      "line_end": 683
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "国师摇头道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 667,
      "line_end": 683
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 667,
      "line_end": 683
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "国师呜咽道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 667,
      "line_end": 683
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通一口唾涎吐了过去，喝道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 667,
      "line_end": 683
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "国师点了点头。周伯通又道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 685,
      "line_end": 705
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n国师心中怅惘，叹道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 685,
      "line_end": 705
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n黄蓉心神稍定，见国师黯然流泪，确是心伤爱女之丧，爱女多半不是他推落谷去，但此事定须有人承责，悲痛之际，不及细思细问，一咬牙，提起手中竹棒，迳向国师扑了过去。\n\n她使个",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "line_start": 685,
      "line_end": 705
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "龙象般若功",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 707,
      "line_end": 723
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "灵台穴",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 725,
      "line_end": 741
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位小心！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 725,
      "line_end": 741
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让开了！\n\n",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 725,
      "line_end": 741
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "泥鳅功",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 725,
      "line_end": 741
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别逃！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "line_start": 743,
      "line_end": 757
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一阳指",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "line_start": 743,
      "line_end": 757
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_da_shi",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一阳指",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 743,
      "line_end": 757
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guo",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两人之名，大吃一惊：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 787,
      "line_end": 803
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guo",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n便在此时，一灯又踏上了半步。半空中双雕也已瞧出了便宜，雌雕大声鸣叫，疾扑而下，直冲国师面门，伸出利爪去挖国师眼珠。\n\n国师骂道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 787,
      "line_end": 803
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "臭和尚，老顽童不讲究什么江湖规矩了。\n\n要来个以二对一。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 805,
      "line_end": 821
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄老邪！这臭和尚害死了你的外孙女儿，快合力擒他！\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 823,
      "line_end": 837
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "中神通和北丐、西毒，谢世已久，这位高僧便是南帝，这一位周兄，是中神通的师弟。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 839,
      "line_end": 853
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "倘若我师兄在世，你焉能接得他的十招？\n\n",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "line_start": 839,
      "line_end": 853
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "单打独斗，老僧谁也不惧。\n\n",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "line_start": 839,
      "line_end": 853
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。今日咱们又不是华山论剑，争那武功天下第一名号，谁来跟你单打独斗？\n\n臭和尚作恶多端，自己裁决了罢。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "line_start": 839,
      "line_end": 853
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "五字，心中一动，抢上去伸臂一挡，架过了他这一掌，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 855,
      "line_end": 873
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "国师昂然道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 855,
      "line_end": 873
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这几句话竟十分诚恳。\n\n国师尚未回答，只听得扑翅声响，那雌雕负了雄雕从深谷中飞上，双雕身上都湿淋淋地，看来谷底是个水潭。\n\n雄雕毛羽零乱，已奄奄一息，右爪仍牢牢抓着国师的红冠。\n\n雌雕放下雄雕后，忽地转身又冲入深谷，再回上来时，背上伏着一人，赫然便是郭襄。\n\n黄蓉惊喜交集，大叫：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 855,
      "line_end": 873
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "至阳穴",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 875,
      "line_end": 889
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "躺下罢！\n\n",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 875,
      "line_end": 889
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这和尚当真厉害，身上连中三下重手，居然仍不摔倒。\n\n",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 875,
      "line_end": 889
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妈，他在下面⋯⋯在下面，快⋯⋯快去⋯⋯救他⋯⋯",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 875,
      "line_end": 889
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不碍事，只受了惊吓。\n\n",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 875,
      "line_end": 889
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 891,
      "line_end": 907
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭襄点了点头，低声道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 891,
      "line_end": 907
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她心中是说：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 891,
      "line_end": 907
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉见女儿全身湿透，问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 891,
      "line_end": 907
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭襄点了点头，闭上双眼，再无力气说话，只伸手指着深谷。\n\n黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 891,
      "line_end": 907
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当下作哨召雕。\n\n但连吹数声，双雕竟不理睬。黄蓉好生奇怪，数十年来，双雕闻唤即至，从不违命，何以今日对自己的口哨直似不闻？\n\n她又一声长哨，只见那雌雕双翅一振，高飞入云，盘旋数圈，悲声哀啼，猛地里从空中疾冲而下。\n\n黄蓉心道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 891,
      "line_end": 907
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大叫：",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "line_start": 891,
      "line_end": 907
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_wu_shuang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "问世间，情是何物，直教生死相许？天南地北双飞客，老翅几回寒暑？\n\n欢乐趣，离别苦，就中更有痴儿女。君应有语，渺万里层云，千山暮雪，只影向谁去？\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 909,
      "line_end": 929
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_ying",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这头雌雕假若不死，此后万里层云，千山暮雪，叫它孤单只影，如何排遣？\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 909,
      "line_end": 929
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师父，师姊，杨大哥既在潭底，咱们怎生救他上来才好？\n\n",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 909,
      "line_end": 929
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "襄儿，谷底是怎生光景？\n\n",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 909,
      "line_end": 929
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我一掉下去，笔直的沉到了水底，心中一慌，吃了好几口水。\n\n后来不知怎的冒上了水面，大哥哥⋯⋯杨大哥拉住我头发，提了我起来⋯⋯",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 909,
      "line_end": 929
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭襄道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 931,
      "line_end": 949
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 931,
      "line_end": 949
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "了一声，问道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 931,
      "line_end": 949
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n郭襄道：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 931,
      "line_end": 949
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guo",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "平安否　盼答",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 951,
      "line_end": 967
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "山谷虽深，计来长索也应已经垂到，待我下去瞧瞧。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 951,
      "line_end": 967
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我先去！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 951,
      "line_end": 967
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "影踪全无，影踪全无，有什么杨过？\n\n连牛过、马过也没有。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "line_start": 969,
      "line_end": 983
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨大哥明明是在下面，怎会不在？\n\n他坐在水边的一棵大树上啊。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "line_start": 969,
      "line_end": 983
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "襄儿，你身子未曾康复，不可下去，别再累妈耽心。\n\n你杨大哥若在底下，咱们这许多人定能救他上来，知道么？\n\n",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "line_start": 969,
      "line_end": 983
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "灵台",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "line_start": 969,
      "line_end": 983
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "巨阙",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "line_start": 969,
      "line_end": 983
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "清冷渊",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "line_start": 969,
      "line_end": 983
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周大哥，你捉只蜜蜂来瞧瞧，看翅上是否有字？\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 985,
      "line_end": 1001
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没字。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 985,
      "line_end": 1001
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一只有字，这一只有字。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 985,
      "line_end": 1001
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我在绝，情谷底",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 985,
      "line_end": 1001
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥哥便不肯上来，外公和妈妈他们抬也抬了他上来。\n\n到底他为什么要自尽呢？难道杨大嫂死了？永远不跟他见面了？\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 1003,
      "line_end": 1021
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸亏我大哥哥没上来，否则你逃也逃不走啦！\n\n",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 1023,
      "line_end": 1035
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊哟、啊哟",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 1023,
      "line_end": 1035
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么？很痛么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 1023,
      "line_end": 1035
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你妈妈点了我背心的灵台穴和胸下巨阙穴，我全身如有千万只蚂蚁在咬，痛痒难当，她为什么不再点了我膻中穴和玉枕穴？\n\n",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 1023,
      "line_end": 1035
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "膻中",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 1023,
      "line_end": 1035
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "玉枕",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 1023,
      "line_end": 1035
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她如点了我膻中、玉枕两穴，我胸背麻木，就可少受许多痛苦。\n\n我这般深厚的修为，难道能要得了我性命？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 1023,
      "line_end": 1035
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n国师道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 1037,
      "line_end": 1057
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "国师道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 1037,
      "line_end": 1057
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭襄道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 1037,
      "line_end": 1057
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n郭襄不住摇头，道：",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "line_start": 1037,
      "line_end": 1057
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "国师急道：",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "line_start": 1037,
      "line_end": 1057
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭襄见他说得诚恳，心想：",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "line_start": 1037,
      "line_end": 1057
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "伸指在他胸口膻中穴上轻轻一点，国师舒了一口气，道：",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "line_start": 1037,
      "line_end": 1057
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭襄便依照父母所传的点穴之法，在他膻中穴上点了一指。\n\n国师道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 1059,
      "line_end": 1077
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "起初仍轻点试探，这才运力而点。\n\n国师道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 1059,
      "line_end": 1077
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "闭目暗暗运气，突然间一跃而起，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 1059,
      "line_end": 1077
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\n\n郭襄大骇，叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 1059,
      "line_end": 1077
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "国师左手一勾，抓住了她手腕，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 1059,
      "line_end": 1077
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说着双足一点，带着郭襄向前奔去。\n\n郭襄大叫：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 1059,
      "line_end": 1077
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好生后悔：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 1059,
      "line_end": 1077
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她怎知这",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 1059,
      "line_end": 1077
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "推你下去，摔死你这恶和尚。\n\n",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 1079,
      "line_end": 1091
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "，真舍不得她又再自尽，不及扯断长索，便向她扑去。\n\n郭襄发足便奔，在山石和大树间纵来跃去。若在平阳之地，国师只须两个起落，早便追上，但断肠崖前到处都是古木怪石，郭襄东一钻，西一躲，一时倒也奈何她不得，跟她捉迷藏般大兜圈子，追了良久，方始使一招",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 1093,
      "line_end": 1103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妈！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 1105,
      "line_end": 1122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小郭襄那里去了？\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 1105,
      "line_end": 1122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可惜，可惜！终于错过了时机！\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 1105,
      "line_end": 1122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小郭襄，小郭襄，你在那里啊？\n\n",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "line_start": 1105,
      "line_end": 1122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师姊，你休担忧，定是那国师挟持襄儿一路南行。\n\n襄儿留下鞋子，好教咱们知道。这孩子聪明机警，实不下于她妈妈呢。\n\n",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 1124,
      "line_end": 1130
    }
  ],
